[30/04/2017 23:11:29] <font color="#ffffff">(Música suave)</font>
[30/04/2017 23:11:34] <font color="#ffffff">Joder, Vero.</font>
[30/04/2017 23:11:36] <font color="#ffffff">Qué bonito.</font>
